org.dataconservancy.packaging.gui.view

Interface PackageGenerationView

  • All Superinterfaces:
    View<PackageGenerationPresenter>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PackageGenerationViewImpl

    public interface PackageGenerationView
extends View<PackageGenerationPresenter>
    The view that shows the package generation screen. This screen allows the user to select package creation options, a directory to save the file to, and the ability to then generate a package. If the package generation is successful the view shows a popup with options for creating another package or starting over.
